OL,3,CScottish charity welcomes funding
OL,4,Cboost to continue community workshops
OL,6,FA mental health charity has welcomed a
OL,7,Ffunding boost from the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment in order to continue
OL,9,Foperating their community workshops.
OL,11,FMoffat Men's Shed is one of hundreds
OL,12,Facross the country that provide an
OL,13,Farea for men to socialise, build
OL,14,Fthings and to talk to each other.
OL,16,FMen's Sheds across the country have
OL,17,Fbeen credited with supporting men
OL,18,Fdealing with loneliness, depression
OL,19,Fand poor mental health.
