OL,6,FPeter Hillhouse the Chair Moffat Men's
OL,7,FShed, said: "When I grew up, we were
OL,8,Fsupposed to be men. The boys were
OL,9,Fsupposed to be strong.
OL,11,F"If you fell and hurt yourself you
OL,12,Fweren't to cry because you're supposed
OL,13,Fto be that strong person.
OL,15,F"When I became disabled, I was stuck
OL,16,Fin the house and when you're sitting
OL,17,Fwatching daytime TV, it becomes like a
OL,18,Fmonotonous routine.
