OL,6,F"So it was affecting me mentally as
OL,7,Fwell as physical problems that I had,
OL,8,Fso it's getting out and meeting
OL,9,Fpeople, having a coffee, even making
OL,10,Fthe things that we make.
OL,12,F"That's made a big difference."
OL,14,FThe Scottish Government had announced
OL,15,Fa withdrawal of funding for men's
OL,16,Fsheds.
OL,18,FA decision which was then reversed in
OL,19,FHolyrood on Tuesday.
