OL,6,FDick Monaghan said supporting the
OL,7,Fsheds isn't just vital for men's
OL,8,Fmental health, but for local community
OL,9,Fprojects too.
OL,11,FHe said: "We do quite a lot of jobs at
OL,12,Fthe moment.
OL,14,F"We do memorial benches, benches that
OL,15,Fyou will see around the town.
OL,17,F"It is an important place for to have
OL,18,Fbecause it allows certain members of
OL,19,Fthe community to re-enter the
OL,20,Fcommunity.
