OL,6,F"This shed we have people who are
OL,7,Flonely, have lost touch with society.
OL,9,F"We have people who are bereaved, who
OL,10,Fare no longer in the community.
OL,12,F"We have people who suffer from mental
OL,13,Fhealth, physical health, who have lost
OL,14,Ftouch with society, and through the
OL,15,Fmen shed, they slowly re-enter
OL,16,Fsociety."
